<br>
To to Feerott and camp the solo tree spectre. <br>
- Use earth pet<br>
   - DS him<br>
   - BO II<br>
-Malase<br>
-Cinderbolt x3<br>
<br>
Really friggen easy - <br>
<br>
1. Buff earth pet with BOII and DS.<br>
2. Send in Earth pet<br>
3. Malase Spec<br>
4. Cinder Bolt x3 and he drops. (If you camp on the hill above him there is a chance you will get double damage due to bug)<br>
<br>
This got me through 40 in 10 hours plus Scythes sell for 11p each, Bronze scythes sell for 3pp each....destroy rusties.PLus the spec drops about 3-5 plat kill and he is on a 5 min. timer.<br>
<br>
The only reason I suggest earth pet is he takes a lot of damage and he roots preventing the spec from running at you when you outdamage pet. Also i recommend having SOW or SOW potion in case some higher lvl idiot desides to pull the specs in the FEAR cave.<br>
<br>
Good Luck and Enjoy, <br>
<br>
Santros MacMagus<br>
Legacy Of Titans<br>
Lvl 43 Mage<br>
The Nameless<br>
